<br />
Problems<br />
<br />
1) Why have a shaman in your group when u can have a Beastlord, thier DPS is 10x better and thier slow is only 10% beind and even if it does get resisted they are melee anyway so them getting agro doesnt mean instant death...<br />
<br />
2) Our healing powers are only used as back up cuz they simply dont heal enough fast enough...<br />
<br />
3) "Hey we have the malise line of spells!"..yup so do mages..and chanters have Tash<br />
<br />
4) Haha! our Poison DoTs and Disease Long term DoTs may not be so hot cuz the enemy gets dropped so fast, thank god i have Bane!  <br />
 ---you begin casting Bane---<br />
 ---Your Bane was resisted---<br />
 DAMN!!, someone wake me up when its cool down is over<br />
<br />
5) SoW was cool till the higher lvls, when everyone has Innate run 3 or SoE<br />
<br />
6) Soandso tells you,'Hey can u MGB Fot7 for us?'<br />
    you tell Soandso,' Sure, lemme mem it'<br />
    Soandso tells you ,' bah nvm, ill just have my twinked shaman alt do it, he already has it up, u can go home now, thankz ;-)'<br />
    you tell Soandso,' I see....'<br />
<br />
7) Well even thou my slow is only a hair better then everyone elses..I still have my AoE slow! <br />
 ---you begin casting Tirgirs insects---<br />
 ---Everything u casted it on resisted, sorry, better just tell the BL to get em, better luck next time kiddo---<br />
 ---The stuff u casted on just killed you, loading bind point---<br />
 <br />
okay those seem to be the most apperant problems, here are some ideas i feel could help shaman become balanced again<br />
<br />
1) F. Avatar is nice but the fact that it only can hit one person at a time and has a nasty cool down makes it...not as effective..I'd Like to see Group based Avatar that mabye isnt as strong, but can be tgb'd, this might help give us a reason to stick around on raids now =p<br />
<br />
2) this problem with our slows only bein slightly better cannot really be helped...we cant nerf the others, not amp ours up cuz..90% slow is a lil nutz, id like to see a slow that would slow 71%(to beat chanters), Do some form of cripple, and a weak snare or mabye even a root<br />
<br />
3) AoE Malo id think would be fun...then our AoE Slow may be more effective<br />
<br />
4) an AA that would enhance DoTs so that, if the DoT did not deal full damage by the time the mob is almost dead, u could click a lil AA ability that would remove the DoT from the mob ad deal 3/4 of whatever damage the DoT had left to do in DD form<br />
<br />
5) Somthing like canni3 at lvl 64 , that is targetable, its seems SoE likes to spread the joy of originally unique ideas to another class so, if we could get a way to twitch mana via a targetable canni, we might be a lil more wanted in that respect, or if this is a no can do i think they should re do acumen so instead of Sta regen which they took off, it gives a slight bit of mana regen or mabye adds to mana pool<br />
<br />
6) or mabye we just cant really keep a good hold on slow advantage anymore so add something new, a Curse type spell that would, as long as the target is effected by it, give the target a % chance of MISSING whatever he has agro on, such as at 44 we get 5%, 54 15%, and 65 25%<br />
<br />
7) as for nukes..im not gonna touch that topic...Id rather the DoT recall idea than a 1200/350 nuke, then we would just start steaming off the wizzies<br />
<br />
Well, those are my ideas, if i had to pick one i favored the most it would have to be the % chance of missing thing....naturally i believe it should havea considerable cool doown time and cost enough mana so u cant kep blasting mindlessly with it..</p>
	
	
	
	
	
